headline: A Fresh Look at AT&T’s Valuation After Third-Quarter Growth and Strategic Updates
summary: AT&T reported its third-quarter results with growth in postpaid phone, fiber, and fixed wireless subscribers, while also reaffirming full-year revenue guidance. Even though earnings and revenue missed estimates, management emphasized market share gains and future positioning. See our latest analysis for AT&T.
